{"tid":2390041,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"而去年的長者死亡率卻創新高，首11個月共錄得46414人口死亡(but 只有177宗死亡個案係武肺)","createTime":"2021-02-01T09:51:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-01T09:51:53.000Z","uid":259520,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"88de4c21c0b4e19c1fe16abe5fc12aae3f58a1bf","tid":2390041,"uid":259520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T09:51:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.hkcd.com/content/2021-01/31/content_1246193.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcd.com%2Fcontent%2F2021-01%2F31%2Fcontent_1246193.html&d=FyOxfEvlGqeE3CGJWKQQl8sFuFiCHHua96MUfZSGoRU%3D&h=3993b0f2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkcd.com/content/2021-01/31/content_1246193.html</a><br />\n<br />\n而去年的長者死亡率卻創新高，首11個月共錄得46414人口死亡，即平均每天有約139人離世<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.news.gov.hk/chi/2021/01/20210131/20210131_114413_194.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.news.gov.hk%2Fchi%2F2021%2F01%2F20210131%2F20210131_114413_194.html&d=FyOxfEvlGqeE3CGJWKQQl8sFuFiCHHua96MUfZSGoRU%3D&h=8e15da96\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.news.gov.hk/chi/2021/01/20210131/20210131_114413_194.html</a><br />\n<br />\n就2019冠狀病毒病疫情的最新發展，截至1月28日，本港的確診個案累計有10,322宗，<br />\n當中包括177宗死亡個案，有9,252名病人在接受治療後已康復出院。<br />\n<br />\n武肺死亡率好能高!!<br />\n小你地班恐懼能,識唔識睇數字.<br />\n<br />\n仲有死個班,其實好多都個頭近."}]}